creator: Squadez
descriptionHtml:
From 15 to 25 September 2022, Societe Generale is holding a new edition of the Move For Youth Challenge for its employees around the world, to support the education and integration of young people. Let’s work as a team to cover 2 million kilometres by walking, running, cycling and taking quizzes.
Alone or in teams, take up sporting challenges (walking, running, cycling) and accumulate kilometers on your Smartphone / Garmin / Fitbit / Strava. Our accumulated efforts will surround the Earth with the Red Ribbon, symbolizing the values of mutual aid and the collective in the fight against AIDS. This event, open to all, allows us to inform about the latest news on prevention and treatment while promoting sport in the quality of life of all. This challenge benefits Sidaction, which finances research programs and associations in France and abroad. Registration and additional information at www.relaisdurubanrouge.fr

From 15 to 25 September 2022, Societe Generale is holding a new edition of the Move For Youth Challenge for its employees around the world, to support the education and integration of young people. Let’s work as a team to cover 2 million kilometres by walking, running, cycling and taking quizzes.
Alone or in teams, take up sporting challenges (walking, running, cycling) and accumulate kilometers on your Smartphone / Garmin / Fitbit / Strava. Our accumulated efforts will surround the Earth with the Red Ribbon, symbolizing the values of mutual aid and the collective in the fight against AIDS. This event, open to all, allows us to inform about the latest news on prevention and treatment while promoting sport in the quality of life of all. This challenge benefits Sidaction, which finances research programs and associations in France and abroad. Registration and additional information at www.relaisdurubanrouge.fr
